Ginger Snaps;;78;;90;;NC;;The story of two outcast sisters, Ginger (Katharine Isabelle) and Brigitte (Emily Perkins), in the mindless suburban town of Bailey Downs. On the night of Ginger's first period, she is savagely attacked by a wild creature. Ginger's wounds miraculously heal but something is not quite right. Now Brigitte must save her sister and save herself.;;Mystery & thriller,Horror;;John Fawcett;;2000;;Emily Perkins,Katharine Isabelle,Kris Lemche,Mimi Rogers,Jesse Moss,Danielle Hampton,Peter Keleghan,John Bourgeois,Christopher Redman,Jimmy MacInnis,Lindsay Leese,Nick Nolan;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ginger_snaps